Data reported back by the interaction space. Displays the interpreted x & y coords, width and height, and domain extents. extentsData is in the form:

```
  {
    x1 = {pixel-space}
    y1 = {pixel-space}
    x2 = {pixel-space}
    y2 = {pixel-space}
    w = {pixels}
    h = {pixels}
    eX = [{domain}, {domain}];
    eY = [{domain}, {domain}];
  }
```

